
Please make sure to add the following dependency to your
build.gradle.kts to enable fuzz testing:

testImplementation ("com.code-intelligence", "jazzer-junit","0.13.0")


We highly recommend using cifuzz with JUnit >=5 to ensure
easy IDE integration. You can add it with the following
dependency to your build.gradle.kts:

testImplementation ("org.junit.jupiter", "junit-jupiter","5.9.0")

For Jacoco coverage reports, please add the jacoco plugin to your build.gradle.kts.

